<refnamediv>
<refname>simplelist.vertical.properties</refname>
<refpurpose>Properties that apply to the layout table generated by simplelist in vertical mode.</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<src:fragment xml:id="simplelist.vertical.properties.frag"><xsl:attribute-set name="simplelist.vertical.properties" use-attribute-sets="normal.para.spacing">
</xsl:attribute-set></src:fragment>
</refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><info><title>Description</title></info>
<para>Properties that apply to the fo:table generated by simplelist
in vertical mode, that is, when <literal>@type="vert"</literal>.
You can change vertical spacing and other attributes.</para>
